As the video continues, you‚Äôll also hear two other original works by Rubio Faviere, specially composed for Songs of Birdland and lovingly dedicated to our two children. These pieces were originally written for jazz ensemble, and I have adapted them for solo piano to create a soft, soothing experience perfect for little ears.
